{"tid":11653,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"[IOS JAILBREAK] 8.2以下安裝LIHKG","createTime":"2016-11-29T11:02:32.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-29T12:30:19.000Z","uid":1351,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b52d02e80757b58f488a4f6a4860e1e9b6acedff","tid":11653,"uid":1351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T11:02:32.000Z","msg":"剛剛用我部朋友部JAILBREAK既iPad ( 8.1 / 12B410 )試下點樣裝到 最低要求8.2 既 LIHKG<br />\n<br />\n 我諗好多人都應該知道，但見無人出post（好似係）就講下<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n事前準備： <br />\n(i) ifile  <br />\n(ii) <a href=\"https://www.theiphonewiki.com/wiki/Firmware\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theiphonewiki.com%2Fwiki%2FFirmware&d=ruuHvkpDPTXA%2B6q4k3%2F6TWN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=737aee5d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.theiphonewiki.com/wiki/Firmware</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n教學 :<br />\n<br />\n1) <br />\n開 ifile <br />\n左上角撳到最上層 &gt; System &gt; Library &gt; CoreServices &gt; SystemVersion.plist<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2) <br />\n撳 SystemVersion.plist 選擇 Property List Viewer<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3)<br />\n改 ProductBuildVersion 同 Product Version <br />\n<br />\n係link到check番自己部機個ProductBuildVersion 同 Product Version <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.theiphonewiki.com/wiki/Firmware\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theiphonewiki.com%2Fwiki%2FFirmware&d=ruuHvkpDPTXA%2B6q4k3%2F6TWN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=737aee5d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.theiphonewiki.com/wiki/Firmware</a><br />\n<br />\n比如我朋友個部係iPad 我就幫佢改成 <br />\nProductBuildVersion : 12D508<br />\nProduct Version : 8.2<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n4)<br />\nrestart 部機<br />\n<br />\n5)<br />\n咁應該入appstore就可以install到個app<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n已知BUG:<br />\n1）開post／回post 會馬上彈app，但post／回覆是正常回到的<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb37be37e736575f592b726dc246d67a70543a6f","tid":11653,"uid":1351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T11:09:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b6374c8c04674e02c9f85ed353253dde5c391c5","tid":11653,"uid":1351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T11:12:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94f9cbed5fa39c14e5b30e31084ab6c7bddc342f","tid":11653,"uid":17550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T11:54:46.000Z","msg":"pish<br />\n<br />\n利申10.1.1"},{"pid":"2602db43d6a01eee810528d5204cb9cf837736e5","tid":11653,"uid":1130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T11:59:32.000Z","msg":"help pish"},{"pid":"208ad96056aedc2f529733900b2b88f337c97da3","tid":11653,"uid":31271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T12:20:06.000Z","msg":"我整左之後都裝唔到,撳完get 之後load 一load 無反應"},{"pid":"4f52b2ca5b3c12f8aa7b91de12e11de228edc08d","tid":11653,"uid":3223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T12:21:26.000Z","msg":"最好唔好改 system version<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n改 app system requirement 好啲"},{"pid":"e51f44086aac0d3202b11bac70120d579fc193e6","tid":11653,"uid":31271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T12:28:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最好唔好改 system version<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n改 app system requirement 好啲</blockquote><br />\n即係點改?"},{"pid":"aff91ae9296620593685432830faeb7d68ab5ad6","tid":11653,"uid":1351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T12:30:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最好唔好改 system version<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n改 app system requirement 好啲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n就咁聽個名好似你個方法好d <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n求教"}]}